28
00:03:06,970 --> 00:03:10,780
Bao Zitou is fighting back now. I suspect that other tribe members have entered the city.

29
00:03:10,780 --> 00:03:15,190
Whether to protect the city or drive out the Falcon Tribe...if General isn't here, there is no one to decide.

30
00:03:15,190 --> 00:03:17,500
Can't you make the decision?

31
00:03:17,990 --> 00:03:21,030
If General isn't here, that is his dereliction of duty.

32
00:03:21,030 --> 00:03:24,210
If the royal court hears of this, he'll be punished!

33
00:03:45,090 --> 00:03:48,050
You all take care of protecting the city. Leave the ones that snuck in to me.

34
00:03:48,050 --> 00:03:50,180
Let's drag out time together and wait for General to return.

35
00:03:50,180 --> 00:03:51,980
All our problems will be solved!

36
00:03:51,980 --> 00:03:53,800
Lady, you are a noble.

37
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:56,300
If you are injured, what will I say to General?

38
00:03:56,300 --> 00:03:58,720
If something happens to General, we'll all die!

39
00:03:58,720 --> 00:04:00,950
Stop nagging, do as I say!

40
00:04:02,370 --> 00:04:04,500
Hurry and go!

41
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:07,260
Yes!

42
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:08,290
<i>It looks like she really isn't a spy.</i>

43
00:05:08,290 --> 00:05:10,880
<i>She was sent by the person secretly helping me.</i>

44
00:05:29,060 --> 00:05:30,640
Search!

45
00:05:48,260 --> 00:05:50,230
<i>They really fell for my trap!</i>

46
00:05:50,230 --> 00:05:53,760
Our people clearly saw Chu Xiuming leave the city. Why is he at home?

47
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:55,750
I'm afraid it's a trap!

48
00:05:56,260 --> 00:05:57,960
Go and take a look!

49
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:24,730
No matter if it's him or not, we must fight to the death today!

50
00:06:24,730 --> 00:06:28,470
Killing Chu Xiuming will earn us great merit! Attack!

51
00:06:35,350 --> 00:06:37,920
<i>This sword is too heavy, I can't lift it!</i>

52
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:40,020
<i>My dagger is much more convenient!</i>

53
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:48,100
He dares to insult us?

54
00:06:48,100 --> 00:06:53,270
Whoever kills Chu Xiuming will earn great merit! Attack!

55
00:07:20,760 --> 00:07:24,220
Put down your weapons! Perhaps I can spare your life!

56
