<i>My Lady, please, this way. Come come come!</i>

68
00:09:14,500 --> 00:09:15,490
Come come come!

69
00:09:15,490 --> 00:09:17,840
Miss, hurry and sit!

70
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,760
Miss, you were too awesome today!

71
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:22,940
Listen to me! We completely defeated the enemy at the city gates today!

72
00:09:22,940 --> 00:09:26,440
The Manor has our Lady, it's has firm as a huge rock.

73
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:29,770
Really! I has been going on the battlefield for so many years!

74
00:09:29,770 --> 00:09:32,300
Put your leg down!

75
00:09:32,300 --> 00:09:35,320
It was my first time to see a woman so brave!

76
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:38,900
-You are too kind!
-Well said!

77
00:09:39,460 --> 00:09:42,630
-Everyone sit down, don't be courteous!
-Okay!

78
00:09:42,630 --> 00:09:45,400
Lady, you were so handsome today!

79
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:49,140
If you were a man, that would be nice. I'd marry you!

80
00:09:49,140 --> 00:09:50,570
I like you too!

81
00:09:50,570 --> 00:09:53,070
I would also like to marry you!

82
00:09:53,070 --> 00:09:54,310
I'll marry you all!

83
00:09:54,310 --> 00:09:56,470
Wait your turn, there's still General!

84
00:09:56,470 --> 00:09:58,830
That's right! There's still General!

85
00:09:58,830 --> 00:10:00,580
Let me tell you.

86
00:10:00,580 --> 00:10:04,310
I could successfully protect the manor today because of all of your help!

87
00:10:04,310 --> 00:10:06,010
It's not just my merit!

88
00:10:06,010 --> 00:10:07,980
Pour me a cup!

89
00:10:08,550 --> 00:10:09,960
Come! Thank you Lady, thank you Lady.

90
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:11,530
Thank you Lady, thank you Lady.

91
00:10:11,530 --> 00:10:12,990
You are too kind!

92
00:10:12,990 --> 00:10:14,700
I will thank you all here!

93
00:10:14,700 --> 00:10:16,240
We are willing to follow Lady!

94
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:17,660
-Follow Lady!
-Follow Lady!

95
00:10:17,660 --> 00:10:19,870
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

96
00:10:22,010 --> 00:10:24,470
Sit, sit! Everyone sit!

97
00:10:24,470 --> 00:10:28,630
Let me tell you! Using the General's sword to counter that Falcon tribe was way too easy!

98
00:10:28,630 --> 00:10:30,400
That's why I pulled out my dagger!

99
00:10:30,400 --> 00:10:34,780
I never imagined they'd even fear a dagger! Don't you think they're cowards?

100
00:10:34,780 --> 00:10:38,150
Let me tell you. I was so scared!

101
00:10:38,150 --> 00:10:41,440
<i>- You didn't see how dangerous it was!
- It really was like this!</i>

102
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:44,080
<i>Fortunately our Lady turned danger in to safety.</i>

103
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:46,440
Xiuyan.

104
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:50,360
Thank you for guarding the city and fighting back the Falcon Tribe today.

105
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:51,980
Thank you.

106
00:10:51,980 --> 00:10:54,550
General, that is my duty.

107
00:10:54,550 --> 00:10:58,860
That's right. I must also thank you for hiding that I wasn't in the city.

108
00:10:58,860 --> 00:11:01,160
I avoided punishment from the court.

109
00:11:02,130 --> 00:11:05,550
That's not my merit.

110
00:11:06,980 --> 00:11:11,000
We were in a crisis then. Lady proposed that I protect the city and she'd protect the manor.

111
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:13,580
She came up with this idea so you wouldn't have failed your duties.

112
00:11:13,580 --> 00:11:16,730
I didn't know about the idea of wearing your armor either.

113
00:11:16,730 --> 00:11:18,680
You're all my soldiers!

114
00:11:21,020 --> 00:11:23,580
General, let's join them?

115
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:26,030
Really? Is it that simple?

116
00:11:26,030 --> 00:11:28,200
I'm going back to my room to rest.

117
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:29,580
Come on. Miss

118
00:11:29,580 --> 00:11:32,160
- Let me fill your cup. 
 - Okay, fill it up.

119
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:34,360
- Come on, fill it up. 
 - Cheers! Cheers!

120
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:37,260
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

121
00:11:40,520 --> 00:11:43,130
Lieutenant General! You earned a lot of merit today too.

122
00:11:43,130 --> 00:11:45,740
Why don't you drink with us?

123
00:11:46,230 --> 00:11:48,620
Guarding the manor was all Lady's merit.

124
00:11:48,620 --> 00:11:50,340
You should celebrate with her.

125
00:11:50,340 --> 00:11:51,710
You earned merit too!

126
00:11:51,710 --> 00:11:56,740
Then, I will thank you for protecting the city on behalf of the people.

127
00:11:56,750 --> 00:11:59,250
Guarding the manor is not my merit alone.

128
00:11:59,250 --> 00:12:02,160
Hurry and celebrate with them. I have to go back to the barracks.

129
00:12:02,160 --> 00:12:05,700
Wait! This is the dessert that I personally made.

130
00:12:05,700 --> 00:12:08,330
If you eat it, all your wishes will definitely come true!

131
00:12:08,330 --> 00:12:09,420
Thank you.

132
00:12:09,420 --> 00:12:11,470
Little Miss Xiao Cong made this?

133
00:12:11,470 --> 00:12:13,170
-I must have a good taste!
-I made it for Lieutenant General!

134
00:12:13,170 --> 00:12:14,530
I'm going back to the barracks.

135
00:12:14,530 --> 00:12:15,810
- Lieutenant General!  
 - How delicious!

136
00:12:15,810 --> 00:12:17,350
Lieutenant General!

137
00:12:17,350 --> 00:12:19,300
Little Miss Xiao Cong.

138
00:12:20,040 --> 00:12:21,440
Little Miss Xiao Cong!

139
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:24,540
Do you like the hairpin I had someone give you a few days ago?

140
00:12:24,540 --> 00:12:28,240
I don't like it! Don't give me anything else in the future.

141
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:30,170
She doesn't like it?

142
00:12:33,570 --> 00:12:36,410
I must have been tricked by that black hearted merchant!

143
00:12:38,290 --> 00:12:41,580
<i>Where's the General? General!</i>

144
00:12:42,220 --> 00:12:44,190
General.

145
00:12:44,190 --> 00:12:45,300
It's so late already.

146
00:12:45,300 --> 00:12:47,190
Is there something you need from me, My Lady?

147
00:12:47,190 --> 00:12:49,960
You're going through such a difficult time.

148
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:52,980
Everyday, you have to put on such heavy armour.

149
00:12:52,980 --> 00:12:54,600
You have to carry such a heavy sword.

150
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:58,570
You have to put on that heavy mask and then you still go out and fight your battles with such confidence and ease.

151
00:12:58,570 --> 00:13:01,820
You've got such a heavy burden to bear!

152
00:13:04,420 --> 00:13:07,070
No one would believe you even if you told the truth.

153
00:13:07,070 --> 00:13:11,550
I'm the only who understands as I've experienced it firsthand.

154
00:13:11,550 --> 00:13:13,320
Your armour is so heavy!

155
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:17,910
Your mask is so heavy and your sword is so heavy...

156
00:13:17,910 --> 00:13:23,860
I truly admire you from the bottom of my heart. You have my deepest sympathies...

157
00:13:23,860 --> 00:13:25,400
My Lady...

158
00:13:25,400 --> 00:13:26,730
Are you listening?

159
00:13:26,730 --> 00:13:30,070
If you need my help, tell me.

160
00:13:30,070 --> 00:13:33,790
It is my duty for the sake of your armor.

161
00:13:34,700 --> 00:13:37,140
I'm <i>blushing with shame</i>

162
00:13:37,140 --> 00:13:39,140
at the fact that My Lady understands me so well.

163
00:13:39,140 --> 00:13:41,060
You deserve to be praised, you deserve to be praised.

164
00:13:41,060 --> 00:13:44,750
The meritorious service I, Shen Jin have rendered must be recognised.

165
00:13:44,750 --> 00:13:48,010
This time when I was guarding the town...

166
00:13:48,010 --> 00:13:50,870
the experience I've had guarding the manor.

167
00:13:50,870 --> 00:13:54,850
I've rendered such a great service to you, you should give me a reward!

168
00:13:54,850 --> 00:13:58,230
You have to agree even if you don't want to!

169
00:13:59,060 --> 00:14:01,100
My Lady, this time you've kept the manor safe on my behalf

170
00:14:01,100 --> 00:14:03,930
and took such a great risk. It must not have been an easy feat for you.

171
00:14:04,530 --> 00:14:07,130
All right. I shall record the service you rendered with reluctance.

172
00:14:07,130 --> 00:14:09,650
What do you mean "with reluctance"?

173
00:14:09,650 --> 00:14:11,300
You should bear in mind that I rendered a <i>great</i> service.

174
00:14:11,300 --> 00:14:13,720
All right, all right. I'll remember that you rendered a great service.

175
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:16,770
Then you... You should reward me for my service.

176
00:14:16,770 --> 00:14:18,800
Haven't I already granted you your freedom?

177
00:14:18,800 --> 00:14:20,850
What other reward do you seek?

178
00:14:23,190 --> 00:14:27,220
Your bed is so soft!

179
00:14:28,310 --> 00:14:32,240
Even your quilt feels much better than mine.

180
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:34,400
My room is too small.

181
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:38,450
Your room is so much nicer.

182
00:14:41,070 --> 00:14:43,820
I don't care anymore. I want to stay in your room.

183
00:14:43,820 --> 00:14:45,710
I don't care even if you disagree to it.

184
00:14:45,710 --> 00:14:48,580
I'm so pitiful! I am!

185
00:14:48,580 --> 00:14:54,080
I've been living in that haunted house for so many days...

186
00:15:04,770 --> 00:15:08,120
All right. I agree to your demands.

187
00:15:08,120 --> 00:15:13,050
Seeing as you've become so drunk, you may sleep here tonight.

188
00:16:14,100 --> 00:16:16,800
<i>Your Majesty, news has arrived from the border.</i>

189
00:16:16,800 --> 00:16:18,750
The Falcon Tribe planned a surprise attack today.

190
00:16:18,750 --> 00:16:23,170
General Chu managed to repel them successfully. However...

191
00:16:24,890 --> 00:16:26,790
What are you trying to say, Lord Liu?

192
00:16:26,790 --> 00:16:29,170
I heard that General Chu was not in the city today

193
00:16:29,170 --> 00:16:31,720
and his wife was the one who kept watch and subdued the Falcon Tribe.

194
00:16:31,720 --> 00:16:35,740
Your Majesty, it is the General's responsibility to protect the city.

195
00:16:35,740 --> 00:16:38,410
How was a mere woman able to keep watch over the manor?

196
00:16:38,410 --> 00:16:41,910
And besides, the border is thousands of miles away.

197
00:16:41,930 --> 00:16:44,850
Not one piece of news reached my ears throughout the entire day,

198
00:16:44,850 --> 00:16:47,600
so how did you come to know of this, Lord Liu?

199
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:50,870
<i>This humble official</i> merely heard it through the grapevine.

200
00:16:50,870 --> 00:16:53,550
General Chu is one of Your Majesty's favourite subjects,

201
00:16:53,550 --> 00:16:56,380
and the General's wife is the young mistress of the Rui Royal Manor.

202
00:16:56,380 --> 00:16:59,340
Even if his actions are inappropriate,

203
00:16:59,340 --> 00:17:01,390
the ministers wouldn't be able to speak out against them.

204
00:17:01,390 --> 00:17:04,400
<i>This humble official</i> has been so bold as to request an audience with Your Majesty.

205
00:17:04,400 --> 00:17:06,730
Lord Liu, you're overanalysing things.

206
00:17:06,730 --> 00:17:08,770
If Yongning Bo were to make a mistake, 
 <i>(Yongning Bo (永宁伯) - Count of Everlasting Peace)</i>

207
00:17:08,770 --> 00:17:11,090
I have my own methods of punishing him.

208
00:17:11,090 --> 00:17:15,220
Your Majesty, General Chu is the best candidate when it comes to defending the border.

209
00:17:15,220 --> 00:17:17,700
He's the one in the Imperial Court who wields military authority.

210
00:17:17,700 --> 00:17:20,880
And he's the only other person besides Your Majesty who is capable of dispatching the troops.

211
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:24,170
<i>This humble official</i> is afraid he will become power-hungry.

212
00:17:24,170 --> 00:17:25,760
<i>He's right, Your Majesty.</i>

213
00:17:25,760 --> 00:17:28,580
If the General's wife is being exploited by the General,

214
00:17:28,580 --> 00:17:30,990
the aftermath will be too horrible to contemplate.

215
00:17:30,990 --> 00:17:32,880
So what do you suggest?

216
00:17:32,880 --> 00:17:37,230
Your Majesty, why don't we send someone to investigate this matter thoroughly?

217
00:17:37,230 --> 00:17:40,590
<i>This humble official</i> will arrange everything.

218
00:17:42,010 --> 00:17:44,260
It isn't appropriate to send someone to investigate them.

219
00:17:45,140 --> 00:17:48,240
I have not seen <i>Yongning Bo</i> for quite some time already.

220
00:17:48,850 --> 00:17:50,210
Send the Court Painter over.

221
00:17:50,210 --> 00:17:52,880
Let the Court Painter observe how our prosperous General

222
00:17:52,880 --> 00:17:55,620
and his wife are living.

223
00:17:56,720 --> 00:17:59,490
Your Majesty, <i>a general planning in the seclusion of his tent</i>

224
00:17:59,490 --> 00:18:02,670
<i>is able to determine the outcome of the distant battle.</i>

225
00:18:16,270 --> 00:18:18,040
- Miss? 
 - My Lady? 
 - My Lady?

226
00:18:18,040 --> 00:18:19,300
- My Lady? 
 - My Lady?

227
00:18:19,300 --> 00:18:20,910
Miss?

228
00:18:23,190 --> 00:18:25,950
My Lady, why are you sleeping on the floor?

229
00:18:25,950 --> 00:18:29,930
It's all right, it's all right. Our Young Miss has never been one to sleep properly.

230
00:18:30,720 --> 00:18:33,040
What are all of you doing?

231
00:18:33,040 --> 00:18:36,190
The General has ordered us to move your luggage and your belongings into this room.

232
00:18:36,190 --> 00:18:39,170
My Lady will be staying here from now on.

233
00:18:39,170 --> 00:18:40,750
He... Did he really say that?

234
00:18:40,750 --> 00:18:42,190
That's correct.

235
00:18:42,190 --> 00:18:43,890
I'm very sure of it.

236
00:18:43,890 --> 00:18:47,970
This is much more comfortable than the other room.

237
00:18:48,540 --> 00:18:52,680
The General's bed is fine and soft.

238
00:19:00,590 --> 00:19:03,880
This is totally a fairyland.

239
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:05,530
Let's move on to another subject.

240
00:19:05,530 --> 00:19:06,920
Before you married into this household,

241
00:19:06,920 --> 00:19:09,110
